  "1871990": {
    "name": "Engine Evolution 2022",
    "steam_appid": 1871990,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1871990/extras/f0035e35b4fd55af2ff8eb1801b2bbc6.poster.avif?t=1727903672\" width=616 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1871990/extras/f0035e35b4fd55af2ff8eb1801b2bbc6.webm?t=1727903672\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1871990/extras/f0035e35b4fd55af2ff8eb1801b2bbc6.mp4?t=1727903672\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>。<br>这款游戏是我在布拉格查尔斯大学学习期间制作的。游戏的大部分内容都是我一个人完成的。希望您会喜欢！我的目标是有一天能在一款游戏中记录 150 年的赛车历史。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1871990/extras/584513228f2b3ebab6795927200fd4b1.poster.avif?t=1727903672\" width=616 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1871990/extras/584513228f2b3ebab6795927200fd4b1.webm?t=1727903672\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1871990/extras/584513228f2b3ebab6795927200fd4b1.mp4?t=1727903672\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>引擎进化是一款多人赛车游戏。<br>引擎进化》是一款多人赛车游戏，其原理类似于《坦克世界》--每次与其他 11 名玩家比赛，您都会获得经验和信用点数，您可以用这些经验和信用点数为您的车辆购买各种升级物品或解锁更新的车辆。从 1906 年的机器开始。您能登上顶峰，驾驶现代机械吗？<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1871990/extras/eb3fac249238e59c486a6f330ba3cfac.poster.avif?t=1727903672\" width=616 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1871990/extras/eb3fac249238e59c486a6f330ba3cfac.webm?t=1727903672\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1871990/extras/eb3fac249238e59c486a6f330ba3cfac.mp4?t=1727903672\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>。<br>本作的操作非常简单，既能让玩家保持骑行的激情，又不会太复杂，让玩家花几个小时就能学会。它的主要重点是让玩家尽可能地享受到赛车格斗的乐趣。游戏的核心是短时间、高动作密度的动态比赛。骑行的感觉很容易让人联想到老游戏；不要指望它是一款硬核模拟器。另一方面，这也不是一款卡丁车赛车游戏--游戏中存在物理因素，你需要牢记这一点。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1871990/extras/c9e2062064d79ea5a4b48baad94d6a22.poster.avif?t=1727903672\" width=616 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1871990/extras/c9e2062064d79ea5a4b48baad94d6a22.webm?t=1727903672\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1871990/extras/c9e2062064d79ea5a4b48baad94d6a22.mp4?t=1727903672\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>- 来自 7 个国家的 90 辆历史名车<br>- 25 条真实赛道和自定义赛道<br>- 1000 多种不同的车辆设置<br>- 100 多种车辆模式<br>- 10 种不同的生物群落<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1871990/extras/fb0a1fedb708de5897de1bf641fb4db7.poster.avif?t=1727903672\" width=616 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1871990/extras/fb0a1fedb708de5897de1bf641fb4db7.webm?t=1727903672\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1871990/extras/fb0a1fedb708de5897de1bf641fb4db7.mp4?t=1727903672\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>。<br>使用简单而丰富的自定义系统，您可以随心所欲地自定义您的车辆和车手。您可以为车辆涂上任何颜色组合或数百种可用图案。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1871990/extras/f7983de52e69b9852759a6ba0a217a37.poster.avif?t=1727903672\" width=616 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1871990/extras/f7983de52e69b9852759a6ba0a217a37.webm?t=1727903672\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1871990/extras/f7983de52e69b9852759a6ba0a217a37.mp4?t=1727903672\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>游戏基于定制的云保存技术。其中包含许多经典的网络游戏功能，如云保存、排行榜、每日任务、成就和统计数据！与其他赛车手一较高下！<br><br><strong>征服研究树！[/b］<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1871990/extras/4c8a0f7eb088f97c14d6f679225e5795.avif?t=1727903672\" width=616 height=1100 /></span></strong>",
